156
00:06:49,087 --> 00:06:52,671
However, we Asians usually use cooler box to keep the soap warm。

157
00:06:53,439 --> 00:06:54,207
To keep the soap warm,

158
00:06:54,463 --> 00:06:55,719
we put it into the oven.

159
00:06:56,255 --> 00:06:57,023
For cooling purposes,

160
00:06:57,279 --> 00:06:58,303
we put it into the fridge.

161
00:06:58,815 --> 00:06:59,583
There's no problem at all!

162
